title: SCAM: Arizona Election Fraud Testimony | Ep 71
description: Steven gives a recap of the most important allegations leveled in yesterday's marathon hearing on Arizona voter fraud. He then highlights the Democrats' flip-flop on election security since 2016. Lastly, he reviews some of the latest news on COVID, including the retracted Johns Hopkins article.
